1
00:00:15,280 --> 00:00:16,080
Stop.

2
00:00:23,720 --> 00:00:24,560
Chief Eunuch.

3
00:00:25,040 --> 00:00:25,880
Did you ask for me?

4
00:00:26,200 --> 00:00:27,200
How long will it take
to get there?

5
00:00:27,840 --> 00:00:28,640
About

6
00:00:29,320 --> 00:00:30,520
half a day away.

7
00:00:30,960 --> 00:00:32,920
We must arrive before nightfall.

8
00:00:33,360 --> 00:00:34,160
But your injury...

9
00:00:34,160 --> 00:00:35,320
Don't make me repeat myself.

10
00:00:36,040 --> 00:00:36,960
Yes, sir.

11
00:01:06,620 --> 00:01:09,940
[Governor's Secret Love]
[Episode 1]

12
00:01:10,260 --> 00:01:15,000
[Longevity Shrine]

13
00:01:15,000 --> 00:01:16,040
Excuse me.

14
00:01:16,840 --> 00:01:17,920
Old Master Wang and Madam Wang.
This way, please.

15
00:01:19,320 --> 00:01:20,440
Come on. Hurry.

16
00:01:21,160 --> 00:01:22,040
Coming through.

17
00:01:22,200 --> 00:01:23,240
Let's go.

18
00:01:26,960 --> 00:01:28,000
Come on.

19
00:01:29,480 --> 00:01:31,760
[Immortal Lady Holy Hall]

20
00:01:34,840 --> 00:01:35,520
Immortal Lady.

21
00:01:36,000 --> 00:01:37,120
Who's out there?

22
00:01:37,720 --> 00:01:38,560
They are here.

23
00:01:39,040 --> 00:01:39,960
Please come in.

24
00:01:42,920 --> 00:01:43,680
Please.

25
00:01:48,540 --> 00:01:50,580
[Immortal Lady Holy Hall]

26
00:02:02,480 --> 00:02:03,120
She is

27
00:02:03,120 --> 00:02:04,680
Immortal Lady Yunjiao.

28
00:02:04,720 --> 00:02:05,640
Greet her now.

29
00:02:07,160 --> 00:02:09,200
Greetings, Immortal Lady Yunjiao.

30
00:02:10,520 --> 00:02:12,160
There's no need for that.

31
00:02:13,480 --> 00:02:15,720
Fengshui,

32
00:02:16,040 --> 00:02:17,960
marriage, or funeral.

33
00:02:18,640 --> 00:02:20,080
I shall answer each of your prayers

34
00:02:20,480 --> 00:02:22,480
genuinely.

35
00:02:28,600 --> 00:02:30,160
What do you want to know?

36
00:02:30,360 --> 00:02:31,200
Ask away.

37
00:02:36,200 --> 00:02:39,120
I was told that you are a soothsayer.

38
00:02:39,200 --> 00:02:40,800
Today, I'm here to ask

39
00:02:40,840 --> 00:02:44,080
about the baby in my wife's belly.
Is it a boy or a girl?

40
00:02:48,920 --> 00:02:50,040
Come here.

41
00:03:01,580 --> 00:03:03,420
[Qian's Residence]

42
00:03:05,760 --> 00:03:08,320
Madam Qian, it's a boy.

43
00:03:08,320 --> 00:03:09,160
Great.

44
00:03:09,160 --> 00:03:13,080
With each generation has a sole son,
now the Qian lineage can continue.

45
00:03:19,640 --> 00:03:21,480
The baby inside her tummy

46
00:03:26,320 --> 00:03:27,440
is a boy.

47
00:03:29,360 --> 00:03:30,040
Excellent.

48
00:03:31,120 --> 00:03:31,920
It's a boy.

49
00:03:32,480 --> 00:03:34,120
Congratulations, Old Master Qian.

50
00:03:38,120 --> 00:03:40,000
Is this a mistake?

51
00:03:40,040 --> 00:03:41,240
My surname isn't Qian.

52
00:03:41,240 --> 00:03:42,440
I'm Wang.

53
00:03:42,680 --> 00:03:45,120
Old Master Qian, are you testing me?

54
00:03:46,720 --> 00:03:48,680
The Qian lineage has only one son
over every generation.

55
00:03:48,800 --> 00:03:49,640
You've been expecting a son

56
00:03:50,240 --> 00:03:52,520
to carry on the family line.

57
00:03:52,880 --> 00:03:54,320
Am I right?

58
00:03:54,880 --> 00:03:56,200
Only one son over every generation?

59
00:03:57,440 --> 00:03:59,120
Old Master Qian?

60
00:04:03,240 --> 00:04:04,680
You're carrying

61
00:04:04,720 --> 00:04:06,720
your cousin brother's spawn?

62
00:04:07,560 --> 00:04:08,680
You assured me

63
00:04:08,680 --> 00:04:09,800
that you two were completely through.

64
00:04:10,160 --> 00:04:12,080
You totally failed my trust.

65
00:04:12,360 --> 00:04:13,800
I'll renounce you.

66
00:04:14,080 --> 00:04:15,720
Return to your Old Master Qian's side.

67
00:04:16,680 --> 00:04:17,800
Old Master, I'm sorry.

68
00:04:17,800 --> 00:04:18,880
Get off of me.

69
00:04:19,800 --> 00:04:20,640
Wang.

70
00:04:20,920 --> 00:04:22,560
Renounce me if you like.

71
00:04:22,720 --> 00:04:24,680
I'm not having a child
for a loser like you.

72
00:04:24,680 --> 00:04:26,000
You bloody charlatan!

73
00:04:28,880 --> 00:04:30,040
Guards!

74
00:04:30,840 --> 00:04:32,360
Get this charlatan!

75
00:04:32,600 --> 00:04:33,640
I won't let her get away.

76
00:04:33,640 --> 00:04:34,360
How dare you beat me.

77
00:04:34,360 --> 00:04:35,480
I'm going to rip off her lips.

78
00:04:35,480 --> 00:04:36,400
Tonight,

79
00:04:36,920 --> 00:04:39,120
I'll tell this to your ancestor!

80
00:04:40,080 --> 00:04:40,640
Hurry.

81
00:04:42,760 --> 00:04:43,280
Move away.

82
00:04:44,160 --> 00:04:45,640
Madam, look.

83
00:04:46,760 --> 00:04:47,760
Go after her.

84
00:04:55,040 --> 00:04:56,000
Green Armored Guards are on duty.

85
00:04:56,240 --> 00:04:57,160
Steer clear.

86
00:04:57,160 --> 00:04:58,280
Leave.

87
00:05:01,640 --> 00:05:03,960
Leave immediately.

88
00:05:25,720 --> 00:05:26,680
Rascal.

89
00:05:26,760 --> 00:05:27,880
Don't you know who I am?

90
00:05:30,720 --> 00:05:31,400
As I said,

91
00:05:31,880 --> 00:05:32,960
steer clear.

92
00:05:33,800 --> 00:05:34,400
Of course.

93
00:05:34,840 --> 00:05:37,040
Except for those who are dead.

94
00:05:37,880 --> 00:05:39,760
Sir, please spare me.

95
00:05:39,840 --> 00:05:40,640
Scram!

96
00:05:57,180 --> 00:05:59,700
[Longevity Shrine]

97
00:06:20,200 --> 00:06:21,240
No one comes in here

98
00:06:21,600 --> 00:06:22,720
without my order.

99
00:06:22,880 --> 00:06:23,720
- Yes, sir.
- Yes, sir.

100
00:06:38,160 --> 00:06:39,720
(Why did I fall asleep?)

101
00:06:43,800 --> 00:06:46,200
(Did Madam Wang send him here?)

102
00:06:46,640 --> 00:06:48,120
(It doesn't seem like it.)

103
00:06:52,080 --> 00:06:53,520
(Let me take a closer look.)

104
00:06:57,040 --> 00:06:58,840
(Why is he holding his belly?)

105
00:07:08,960 --> 00:07:10,880
(Is he taking off his clothes now?)

106
00:07:11,920 --> 00:07:13,080
(By the way,)

107
00:07:13,360 --> 00:07:15,320
(a quick glance should be fine.)

108
00:07:51,120 --> 00:07:51,600
Just now,

109
00:07:52,320 --> 00:07:53,240
what did you see?

110
00:07:53,440 --> 00:07:55,760
Is there anything I can't see?

111
00:07:55,760 --> 00:07:58,000
Give me a hint.

112
00:08:04,720 --> 00:08:06,160
So you saw everything.

113
00:08:15,640 --> 00:08:17,160
You asked for this.

114
00:08:45,400 --> 00:08:46,640
[Mu]

115
00:08:50,200 --> 00:08:52,280
This is the most precious thing
my father left for me.

116
00:08:52,280 --> 00:08:53,160
Take this.

117
00:08:53,160 --> 00:08:54,760
I'll come back to you.

118
00:08:55,240 --> 00:08:57,320
Sure. I'll keep it well

119
00:08:57,880 --> 00:08:58,800
while waiting for you.

120
00:09:00,360 --> 00:09:01,400
Mutou.

121
00:09:16,040 --> 00:09:17,360
[Mu]

122
00:09:56,960 --> 00:09:57,600
Slowly.

123
00:09:58,240 --> 00:09:59,520
I'm going to undress you.

124
00:09:59,520 --> 00:10:00,680
Please don't take me wrong.

125
00:10:00,880 --> 00:10:03,000
I'm not taking advantage of you.

126
00:10:04,160 --> 00:10:05,160
Cut your crap.

127
00:10:11,880 --> 00:10:13,680
(This guy is fierce
although he's wounded.)

128
00:10:15,120 --> 00:10:17,120
Your injury is too deep.

129
00:10:17,560 --> 00:10:19,760
Hadn't you encountered me,

130
00:10:19,880 --> 00:10:22,120
you would've gone into the light.

131
00:10:36,440 --> 00:10:37,920
Bear with it.

132
00:10:37,920 --> 00:10:39,640
It might hurt a bit.

133
00:10:48,360 --> 00:10:49,280
I...

134
00:10:50,440 --> 00:10:51,560
I'm back.

135
00:10:51,560 --> 00:10:52,720
What?

136
00:10:53,760 --> 00:10:55,240
You're still alive.

137
00:10:55,920 --> 00:10:56,880
What a relief.

138
00:10:59,600 --> 00:11:00,640
What?

139
00:11:03,240 --> 00:11:04,280
Does it hurt?

140
00:11:05,320 --> 00:11:06,440
It'll be all right.

141
00:11:06,640 --> 00:11:07,840
If it hurts,

142
00:11:08,000 --> 00:11:09,480
how about I sing you a song?

143
00:11:10,400 --> 00:11:11,320
I'll sing for you.

144
00:11:11,560 --> 00:11:12,640
Ignore the pain.

145
00:11:15,520 --> 00:11:19,040
♪Winter breathes plum blossom scent♪

146
00:11:20,000 --> 00:11:23,520
♪Virgin snow drapes a veil of frost♪

147
00:11:24,930 --> 00:11:28,970
♪Lights peep through blooms and leaves♪

148
00:11:29,000 --> 00:11:34,440
♪Like fireflies♪

149
00:11:34,640 --> 00:11:39,280
♪That illuminate the night♪

150
00:11:39,280 --> 00:11:43,580
♪Ushering you into the slumberland♪

151
00:11:43,940 --> 00:11:48,420
♪Like a forever aglow candle♪

152
00:11:48,500 --> 00:11:53,380
♪Radiating within your heart♪

153
00:11:56,900 --> 00:11:57,940
You're awake.

154
00:12:05,600 --> 00:12:07,080
Did you see my body?

155
00:12:08,680 --> 00:12:11,080
Your wound has spread to your thigh.

156
00:12:11,280 --> 00:12:11,960
If I hadn't saved you,

157
00:12:11,960 --> 00:12:13,080
you might've become a eunuch.

158
00:12:13,480 --> 00:12:14,040
You...

159
00:12:15,600 --> 00:12:17,200
What do you want to say?

160
00:12:17,360 --> 00:12:18,040
Anyway, you're awake now.

161
00:12:18,360 --> 00:12:19,280
I should get going.

162
00:12:20,320 --> 00:12:20,920
Stop right there.

163
00:12:24,800 --> 00:12:25,880
Do you think you can leave

164
00:12:26,160 --> 00:12:27,520
after seeing my body?

165
00:12:27,800 --> 00:12:29,360
(I knew you were an ungrateful one.)

166
00:12:32,760 --> 00:12:34,120
You ungrateful brat.

167
00:12:34,680 --> 00:12:36,280
Don't think for a second

168
00:12:36,520 --> 00:12:37,760
you can take my life.

169
00:13:08,600 --> 00:13:13,280
Long live Chief Eunuch!

170
00:13:15,480 --> 00:13:16,560
(Chief Eunuch?)

171
00:13:16,560 --> 00:13:17,400
(He's a eunuch?)

172
00:13:17,960 --> 00:13:18,800
(A fake eunuch?)

173
00:13:20,200 --> 00:13:22,680
(I actually saw the body
of a fake eunuch.)

174
00:13:23,520 --> 00:13:25,440
(I'm so screwed.)

175
00:13:28,740 --> 00:13:33,460
♪Wind and rain escape grasp♪

176
00:13:34,940 --> 00:13:39,620
♪The enticing illusion feels elusive♪

177
00:13:40,340 --> 00:13:43,380
♪Two clouds chance upon each other♪

178
00:13:43,700 --> 00:13:46,500
♪Yet fall out as snow eventually♪

179
00:13:46,900 --> 00:13:52,540
♪They drift down upon past memories♪

180
00:13:53,460 --> 00:13:58,460
♪I blame the limited time
for limitless love♪

181
00:13:59,380 --> 00:14:04,420
♪I frown upon the fate
that brings us close but sets us apart♪

182
00:14:05,020 --> 00:14:08,340
♪Grieves well up♪

183
00:14:08,340 --> 00:14:11,220
♪For this sad departure♪

184
00:14:12,060 --> 00:14:16,820
♪Love happens
before the destined separation♪

185
00:14:16,980 --> 00:14:22,780
♪I resent that the blossom
cannot outlive the autumn♪

186
00:14:23,260 --> 00:14:28,940
♪I wish the scent still lingers
around your fingertip♪

187
00:14:29,340 --> 00:14:32,860
♪I ask not for a shared life with you♪

188
00:14:32,860 --> 00:14:35,860
♪But I yearn for a love♪

189
00:14:36,220 --> 00:14:41,340
♪That carries on beyond time♪

190
00:14:41,340 --> 00:14:48,180
♪A heart trapped in obsessions♪

191
00:14:48,660 --> 00:14:54,060
♪Shall break free at long last♪
